se rats\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"a cry-laughing emoji\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also posted the reporter's message to him, complete with her phone number, in what could be seen as a breach of her privacy.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reporter's message\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"her phone number\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"a breach\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"her privacy\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dennis's first post featured a close-up photo of a Ventum bicycle, accompanied by a hundred-points emoji.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dennis's first post\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"a close-up photo\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"a Ventum bicycle\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a hundred-points emoji\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ventum cycles are top-of-the-line, with some models retailing for up to $17,500.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ventum cycles\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the-line\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"some models\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday morning, Dennis posted a photo appearing to show his son and daughter riding their bikes on a suburban street, with the caption 'Two absolute weapons'.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday morning\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"their bikes\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"a suburban street\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"Two absolute weapons\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also posted a video show reporters with a camera crew trying to film over the back fence of his house.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video show reporters\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"a camera crew\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the back fence\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"his house\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The words they put in your mouth is amazing.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The words\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"your mouth\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Love you guys over at @channel7 @7newsadelaide it was great being able to wish you a great day,' Dennis captioned the post.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"@channel7\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the post\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will never forget how poorly and inappropriately you spoke in front of my daughter at the airport.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"the airport\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us see you release that footage.\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"that footage\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I wish you all the best.'\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dennis (pictured with Hoskins) walked free from court in May 2025 after pleading guilty to an aggravated charge of creating likelihood of harm Pictured: Dennis's first post since the tragedy, featuring a top-of-the-line Ventum bicycle On Thursday morning the former world champion cyclist posted this image appearing to show his son and daughter on their bikes, describing them as 'two absolute weapons' The post featuring the Porsche saw Dennis get slammed by South Australian Victims' Rights Commissioner Sarah Quick.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2778, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Hoskins\", \"score\": 0.9999999993669917, \"rank\": 6.324916808449983e-10, \"text\": \"Hoskins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Hoskins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Hoskins\"}, {\"begin\": 3186, \"end\": 3193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porsche\", \"score\": 0.9999999985866452, \"rank\": 1.1086472818019997e-09, \"text\": \"Porsche\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porsche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porsche\"}, {\"begin\": 3226, \"end\": 3236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9952518858121017, \"rank\": 0.003709986550301248, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"score\": 0.9638562434403772, \"rank\": 0.03749826968444414, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Platt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"an aggravated charge\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"likelihood\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"harm\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis's first post\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"the tragedy\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"the-line\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday morning\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"the former world champion cyclist\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"their bikes\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"two absolute weapons\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3158}, {\"ngram\": \"The post\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"Dennis\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is a deeply offensive comment that demonstrates a clear lack of insight into the real and lasting impact of the harm he has caused,' Quick said.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a deeply offensive comment\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear lack\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"the real and lasting impact\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"the harm\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"Quick\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that the comment indicated 'a profound lack of respect for Melissa and her family'.\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Hastings\", \"score\": 0.6986680945073588, \"rank\": 0.3352806